ğŸ”‘ Step 7: Unlock Jenkins
Retrieve the initial admin password:
```
sudo cat /var/lib/jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword
```
Copy the password and paste it into the browser.


ğŸ§© Step 9: Install Suggested Plugins
After logging in:
    1. Select â€œInstall suggested pluginsâ€
    2. Wait for installation to complete.


ğŸ‘¤ Step 10: Create First Admin User
After plugins install:
    . Set username
    . Set password
    . Enter Full name & email
    . Click Save and Continue
Then click â€œStart using Jenkinsâ€



âš™ï¸ Step 11: Configure Jenkins URL
